{"tid":164122,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)移魂都市 空中監獄 KISSASS1-2","createTime":"2017-03-20T12:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T19:33:48.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c72b4787b67ab33d974f0d2eaf07e10af2b1888","tid":164122,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:44:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e0210858\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=761e45c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9c/Dark_City_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9c%2FDark_City_poster.jpg&h=3af8ef16&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/1/1d/Conairinternational.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F1%2F1d%2FConairinternational.jpg&h=43d6f554&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/30/Kick-Ass_film_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F30%2FKick-Ass_film_poster.jpg&h=f16cf64b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/56/Kick-Ass2-Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F56%2FKick-Ass2-Poster.jpg&h=9516d1fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.約翰&middot;梅鐸一覺醒來，發現自己身邊躺著一具赤裸的女屍，而且自己不但成了嫌疑犯，還無法記起自己的身份。甚至無法認出自己的妻子，在躲避警方和一夥神秘人 追捕的過程中，約翰慢慢接近了事情的真相。原來，黑暗城市是一個外星人的實驗基地，每到子夜時分外星人便會改變城市的形態，並把人們的記憶互相交換，以來研究人類的靈魂..<br />\n<br />\n2.八年前，自海軍陸戰隊受訓完畢的卡麥倫&middot;坡（尼可拉斯&middot;凱吉飾）為了保護剛懷孕的妻子免於小混混的騷擾，犯下了過失致死罪而被判了十年徒刑，在獄中表現良好的他，終於在女兒八歲生日當天獲得假釋，卡麥倫希望能親自將生日禮物送到女兒手中，因此要求典獄官讓他登上囚犯專機&mdash;&mdash;「空中監獄」，以節省返家的時間。但這架「空中監獄」正巧載著一批全美最殘暴兇狠的犯人，準備運送到另一個剛落成的高度保全監獄去<br />\n<br />\n3.平凡無奇的青少年戴夫&middot;萊佐斯基（Dave Lizewski，亞倫&middot;強森飾）想知道在現實生活中，為何沒人想成為漫畫裡的超級英雄。他與好友在被惡霸劫奪時，旁觀者卻無所作為，戴夫決心成為一個真實的超級英雄。他從eBay買件綠色緊身衣作為服裝，裝扮成打擊犯罪的蒙面英雄，儘管沒有任何超能力及接受各種訓練..<br />\n<br />\n4.戴夫&middot;萊佐斯基（亞倫&middot;強森 飾）不再以「屌爆俠」身份打擊犯罪後過上了無聊的生活，開始接受「超殺女」明蒂&middot;麥奎迪（克蘿伊&middot;摩蕾茲 飾）的訓練成為英雄角色。意外殺死母親的克里斯&middot;達米柯（克里斯托福&middot;敏茲-普雷斯 飾）被家族的錢控制，將自己重塑為超級惡棍「臭B王」，發誓要報復屌爆俠。監護人馬庫斯（莫里斯&middot;錢雷諾 飾）發現明蒂仍在打擊罪犯，要她發誓放棄這種行為。戴夫的女友凱蒂&middot;多瑪（琳德茜&middot;馮塞卡 飾）已經注意到戴夫的怪異行為，認為他跟明蒂（她告訴凱蒂自己曾騙過戴夫）聯手欺騙他，於是跟他分手..<br />\n<br />\n9 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa73633b738842cd80e0d68a3086c47df6d4610a","tid":164122,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a18f19a7c87182d68067ced1857851c5330c90","tid":164122,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527ccc14eacd627d9e5c42fb0c7c486883eb6aae","tid":164122,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ede52d5c4dbb4b30f19a